  "accepted_ascii_heavy_residuals": [
    {
      "item_id": "45af1e58e5:0",
      "text": "安装 Tractor、customized 你的 configuration files，并启动 engine 和 blade services 后，就可以提交你的 first job。",
      "ascii_letters": 62,
      "cjk_chars": 16
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45af1e58e5:1",
      "text": "打开 Dashboard 的操作步骤（Open a Dashboard）",
      "ascii_letters": 23,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45af1e58e5:4",
      "text": "http://tractor-engine",
      "ascii_letters": 17,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45af1e58e5:6",
      "text": "http://HOSTNAME:PORT",
      "ascii_letters": 16,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45af1e58e5:7",
      "text": "（如果你有 custom hostname 和 port），然后 login 到 Tractor。",
      "ascii_letters": 30,
      "cjk_chars": 8
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45af1e58e5:8",
      "text": "如果无法访问 Dashboard，请检查 engine 实际上是否正在运行。engine log file 可以提供有用的 diagnostic information。",
      "ascii_letters": 49,
      "cjk_chars": 25
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45af1e58e5:9",
      "text": "示例使用说明（About the Examples）",
      "ascii_letters": 16,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45af1e58e5:10",
      "text": "以下 examples 假定你的 current directory 是 INSTALL_DIR/bin。",
      "ascii_letters": 37,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45af1e58e5:11",
      "text": "TRACTOR_ENGINE environment variable 或 --engine flag 可用于把 command line programs 指向与默认值不同的 engine，或指向通过",
      "ascii_letters": 67,
      "cjk_chars": 19
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45af1e58e5:12",
      "text": "engine discovery",
      "ascii_letters": 15,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45af1e58e5:14",
      "text": "提交作业步骤（Submit a Job）",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45af1e58e5:15",
      "text": "Jobs 可以提交到 Tractor queue，方式包括使用 tractor-spool script、RenderMan for Maya plug-in，或使用",
      "ascii_letters": 56,
      "cjk_chars": 14
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45af1e58e5:16",
      "text": "author API（作业创作 API）",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 4
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45af1e58e5:17",
      "text": "提交到 Tractor queue。Job submission 有时也称为",
      "ascii_letters": 25,
      "cjk_chars": 8
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45af1e58e5:18",
      "text": "spooling",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45af1e58e5:19",
      "text": "，这是类比 print spooling 或传统 batch job systems 的说法。",
      "ascii_letters": 28,
      "cjk_chars": 10
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45af1e58e5:20",
      "text": "tractor-spool 最常把一个",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45af1e58e5:21",
      "text": "Alfred-syntax job file（Alfred 语法作业文件）",
      "ascii_letters": 25,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45af1e58e5:22",
      "text": "的 filename（文件名）作为 argument（参数）。",
      "ascii_letters": 16,
      "cjk_chars": 8
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45af1e58e5:23",
      "text": "下面的 example job 可以放入一个 file 中，并用 tractor-spool 提交。它只会输出 command 运行所在的 environment。",
      "ascii_letters": 44,
      "cjk_chars": 24
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45af1e58e5:24",
      "text": "你可以使用 Dashboard 查看 task 的 output，也可以在 command line 中使用 tq。job id JOBID 应替换为 tractor-spool 输出的 job id。",
      "ascii_letters": 59,
      "cjk_chars": 22
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45af1e58e5:25",
      "text": "-c option 会为剩余 arguments 指定的 single command 创建一个新的 tractor job。试运行这个 simple command 来测试 system 是否正常工作。job status 和 output 可以在 Dashboard 或 tq 中检查。",
      "ascii_letters": 84,
      "cjk_chars": 35
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45af1e58e5:26",
      "text": "删除作业步骤（Delete a Job）",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45af1e58e5:27",
      "text": "可以在 Dashboard 中点击 job queue 中的 job entry，然后按",
      "ascii_letters": 25,
      "cjk_chars": 11
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45af1e58e5:30",
      "text": "Backspace 退格键按键",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45af1e58e5:32",
      "text": "也可以在 command-line 中使用 spooling tool，并通过 --jdelete 指定 job id 来删除 jobs。",
      "ascii_letters": 39,
      "cjk_chars": 15
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45af1e58e5:33",
      "text": "tq 也允许从 command-line 删除 job。",
      "ascii_letters": 16,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45af1e58e5:34",
      "text": "Further Reading（进一步阅读）",
      "ascii_letters": 14,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45af1e58e5:36",
      "text": "Dashboard",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45af1e58e5:37",
      "text": "section 感兴趣，该 section 描述用于管理 system 的 graphical interface。",
      "ascii_letters": 38,
      "cjk_chars": 11
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45af1e58e5:38",
      "text": "Developers（开发人员）可以在",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45af1e58e5:39",
      "text": "Job Author Python API",
      "ascii_letters": 18,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45af1e58e5:40",
      "text": "section 中学习如何生成 job scripts。用于 querying 和 managing jobs 与 blades 状态的 tools 可以用",
      "ascii_letters": 48,
      "cjk_chars": 17
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45af1e58e5:41",
      "text": "Query Python API",
      "ascii_letters": 14,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45af1e58e5:43",
      "text": "Wranglers、admins，以及其他熟悉 command line 的用户，会喜欢 command line tool",
      "ascii_letters": 41,
      "cjk_chars": 12
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45af1e58e5:47",
      "text": "Configuration",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "45af1e58e5:48",
      "text": "section 中探索 advanced customization techniques。",
      "ascii_letters": 38,
      "cjk_chars": 3
    }
  ],
